window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>“We’re here to assist with your transition to Featherstone Academy.”</b></p> <p>Suddenly thrown into a world representing bloodlines I know nothing about, forcing a past I refuse to remember into the present, my world is turned upside down. It doesn’t matter that I didn’t want to go to college; it doesn’t matter that I don’t want to be here. I’ll follow the rules or risk my life. The organization that runs the criminal underworld is no joke.</p> <p>Apparently, I’m an Ace now, but few are happy about my arrival. Secrets have me wanting to run for the hills. Boys have curly hair, skull tattoos, big mouths, and gentle caresses. A diamond has me wanting to make the world a better place. For a lone ranger, my small world just got bigger. What am I willing to do to survive?</p> <p><b>This is a reverse harem romance that includes foul language, sexual scenes, and some M/M. Recommended for mature listeners.</b></p>"; 
